0aa27fa81412c38e71104033713cbc2b4e5ab587.query:
SELECT timestamp, up
                    FROM gateway_ipv4_status
                    JOIN gateway_details
                    ON gateway_ipv4_status.gateway_details_id = gateway_details.id
                    WHERE gateway_details.pub_key=?;
